## Notes
- `OrderDraftService` no longer applies stock math directly; it delegates to policy service.
- `BULK_WEIGHT` reserves by decrementing `product.stockBaseGrams` and releases grams on payment failure/cancel/expiry.
- `PER_VARIANT` retains legacy reservation semantics (`stock_available` down, `stock_reserved` up; release reverses).
- Customer catalog/detail surfaces continue suppressing stock counters for shopper-facing UI.

